By leveling up

Level Ability Cost Description
1 Blaze 13 Powers up Fire-type moves when the Pokémon's HP is low.
10 Heatproof 2 The heatproof body of the Pokémon halves the damage from Fire-type moves that hit it.
25 Illuminate 11 Raises the Pokémon's evasiveness.
40 Flame Body 27 Contact with the Pokémon may burn the attacker.
55 Anger Point 27 The Pokémon is angered when it takes a critical hit, and that maxes its Attack stat.
70 White Smoke 52 The Pokémon's white smoke prevents other Pokémon from lowering its stats.
85 Solar Power 59 Boosts the Sp. Atk stat in harsh sunlight or solar wind, but HP decreases every turn.
100 Dragon's Maw 27 Powers up Dragon-type moves.

  • Italic indicates hidden ability if multiple abilities are disabled
